<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - NGC upgraded.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - NGC upgraded.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Merrill Lynch said it upgraded NGC Corp to near-term attractive from neutral.</p>
<p>-- said it kept NGC as a long-term buy.</p>
<p>-- Additional details were not immediately available.</p>
